1558329-a.title: 50 East 78th Street (Madison Avenue - Park Avenue)

714551f-a.text:
103-113 East 78th Street, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of Park Avenue about 1911.
Neg #2658

722343f-a.text:
880-886 Park Avenue, west side, between 78th and 79th Streets. The parlor store of No. 880 is kept by Eugene Clark, Fish Dealer. 878, not shown on the picture, is the corner house; -- from 878 to P188 inclusive the houses will be demolished in 1926 to make room for the new 888 Park Avenue apartment house.
1922.
0ift of E. M. Jenks.
